*TM:* And I would also say the other thing we=E2=80=99re excited about is, =
also the demands on our software is showing up. So instead of something tha=
t is, now I have incremental efficiency in implementing a nineties on-prem =
data stack using cloud compute with what I expect from data, now we have CE=
Os saying, =E2=80=9CShoot, this tech got scary. I need this for what I thin=
k will be the survival of my institution over the next five years.=E2=80=9D=
 That=E2=80=99s a market that=E2=80=99s very compelling for us, because we=
=E2=80=99re built to sign up for that accountability.

*Is there a bit where you are worried about your addressable market, in tha=
